coords :: Surface -> [Coord]
coords ls = concat $ zipWith lineCoords [0..] ls
    where
    lineCoords y l = lineCoords' y 0 l
    lineCoords' y x "" = []
    lineCoords' y x ('1':cs) = (x,y):lineCoords' y (x+1) cs
    lineCoords' y x (_:cs) = lineCoords' y (x+1) cs

adjust :: [Coord] -> [Coord]
adjust cs = minX `seq` minY `seq` map (`sub` (minX,minY)) cs
    where
    minX = minimum $ map fst cs
    minY = minimum $ map snd cs
    (ax,ay) `sub` (bx,by) = (ax-bx,ay-by)

class Surface
  def initialize
    results = []
    @map = Array.new(8).map{Array.new(8,0)}

    while input = $stdin.gets 
      if input =~ /\d/
        @map[0] = input.chomp.split('')
        7.times do |n|
          @map[n+1] = $stdin.gets.chomp.split('')
        end

        results << check
      end
    end

    results.each do |ans|
      puts ans
    end
  end

  def check_bc(x,y)
    begin
      if @map[y+1][x] == "1"
        return "B"
      else
        return "C"
      end
    rescue
      return "C"
    end
  end

  def check_def(x,y)
    begin
      if @map[y][x+1] == "1"
        return "E"
      elsif @map[y+1][x-1] == "1"
        return "D"
      else
        return "F"
      end
    rescue
      return "D"
    end
  end

  def check_ag(x,y)
    begin
      if @map[y+1][x-1] == "1"
        return "G"
      else
        return "A"
      end
    rescue
      return "A"
    end
  end

  def check
    0.upto(7) do |y|
      0.upto(7) do |x|
        if @map[y][x] == "1"
          case get_around(x,y)
          when 1
            return check_bc(x,y)
          when 2
            return check_def(x,y)
          when 3
            return check_ag(x,y)
          end
        end
      end
    end
  end
  
  def range_check(x,y)
    0 <= x && x < 8 && 0 <= y && y < 8
  end

  def get_around(x,y)
    count = 0
    (y-1).upto(y+1) do |ypos|
      (x-1).upto(x+1) do |xpos|
        if range_check(xpos,ypos) && xpos != x || ypos != y
          count += 1 if @map[ypos][xpos] == "1"
        end
      end
    end
    return count
  end
end

	for dx in 0 .. (w-1)
		xx = x + dx
		if xx >= 8 then
			return false
		end
		for dy in 0 .. (h-1) do
			yy = y + dy

class Map
  FIGURES = {
    A: [
              [0, 1],
      [1, 0], [1, 1]
    ],
    B: [
      [1, 0],
      [2, 0],
      [3, 0]
    ],
    C: [
      [0, 1], [0, 2], [0, 3]
    ],
    D: [
      [1, -1], [1, 0],
      [2, -1]
    ],
    E: [
      [0, 1],
      [1, 1], [1, 2]
    ],
    F: [
      [1, 0], [1, 1],
              [2, 1]
    ]
  }

  def initialize(lines)
    @map = Array.new($HEIGHT + 4) {Array.new($WIDTH + 4, -1)}

    lines.each.with_index(1) do |row, i|
      row.each_char.with_index(1) do |c, j|
        @map[i][j] = c.to_i
      end
    end

    @figures = Hash[
      FIGURES.map {|name, cells| [name, figure?(cells)]}
    ]
  end

  def determine_figure
    (1..$HEIGHT).each do |i|
      (1..$WIDTH).each do |j|
        if @map[i][j] == 1
          @figures.each do |name, det|
            return name if det[i, j]
          end
        end
      end
    end

    nil
  end

  private
  # その形状であるかを返す lambda を返す。
  # 返された lambda には基準となる位置の i, j を渡す。
  #
  # [cells]
  # 1 でなければならない相対位置 [i_r, i_j] の配列
  def figure?(cells)
    lambda {|i, j|
      cells.map {|i_r, j_r| @map[i + i_r][j + j_r]}.all? {|v| v == 1}
    }
  end
end

class Surface
  def initialize
    results = []
    @map = Array.new(8).map{Array.new(8,0)}

    while input = $stdin.gets 
      if input =~ /\d/
        @map[0] = input.chomp.split('')
        7.times do |n|
          @map[n+1] = $stdin.gets.chomp.split('')
        end

        results << check
      end
    end

    results.each do |ans|
      puts ans
    end
  end

  def check_bc(x,y)
    begin
      if @map[y+1][x] == "1"
        return "B"
      else
        return "C"
      end
    rescue
      return "C"
    end
  end

  def check_def(x,y)
    begin
      if @map[y][x+1] == "1"
        return "E"
      elsif @map[y+1][x-1] == "1"
        return "D"
      else
        return "F"
      end
    rescue
      return "D"
    end
  end

  def check_ag(x,y)
    begin
      if @map[y+1][x-1] == "1"
        return "G"
      else
        return "A"
      end
    rescue
      return "A"
    end
  end

  def check
    0.upto(7) do |y|
      0.upto(7) do |x|
        if @map[y][x] == "1"
          case get_around(x,y)
          when 1
            return check_bc(x,y)
          when 2
            return check_def(x,y)
          when 3
            return check_ag(x,y)
          end
        end
      end
    end
  end
  
  def range_check(x,y)
    0 <= x && x < 8 && 0 <= y && y < 8
  end

  def get_around(x,y)
    count = 0
    (y-1).upto(y+1) do |ypos|
      (x-1).upto(x+1) do |xpos|
        if xpos != x || ypos != y && range_check(xpos,ypos)
          count += 1 if @map[ypos][xpos] == "1"
        end
      end
    end
    return count
  end
end

    ],
    F: [
      [0, 0],
      [1, 0], [1, 1],
              [2, 1]
    ]
  }

  def initialize(lines)
    @map = Array.new($HEIGHT + 2) {Array.new($WIDTH + 2, -1)}

    lines.each.with_index(1) do |row, i|
      row.each_char.with_index(1) do |c, j|
        @map[i][j] = c.to_i
      end
    end

    @figures = Hash[
      FIGURES.map {|name, cells| [name, figure?(cells)]}
    ]
  end

  def determine_figure
    (1..$HEIGHT).each do |i|
      (1..$WIDTH).each do |j|
        if @map[i][j] == 1
          @figures.each do |name, det|
            return name if det[i, j]
          end
        end
      end
    end

    nil
  end

  # その形状であるかを返す lambda を返す。
  # 返された lambda には基準となる位置の i, j を渡す。
  #
  # [cells]
  # 1 でなければならない相対位置 [i_r, i_j] の配列
  def figure?(cells)
    lambda {|i, j|
      cells.map {|i_r, j_r| @map[i + i_r][j + j_r]}.all? {|v| v == 1}
    }
  end
end
